msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroZora_Desc"
msgid ""
"The scattered One-Hit Obliterator led you to a\n"
"location where a stone monument with a map of\n"
"trials appeared. Kass's song seems related...\n"
"\n"
"One, <1.se_co>find what the light's path shows<2.re_co>.\n"
"Two, <3.se_co>conquer the ancient foes<4.re_co>.\n"
"Three, <5.se_co>chase rings of the waterfall<6.re_co>.\n"
"Champion, the trials call!\n"
"\n"
"You still have <7.se_co>three<8.re_co> trials to complete."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
